Hi,

Does anyone know if support for the 19" Samsung 960 BF monitor is planned for
ddccontrol anywhere in the near future? 
This monitor
(http://www.samsung.com/Products/Monitor/LCD_Digital/LS19HJDQHVXAA.asp) is one
of the most stunning I have ever seen and I would really like to buy one. 

I have to be able to configure it from linux though, that's why I'm asking.

Best regards
Daniel Liliegren
http://www.gurugonenoob.com


