  osd path: color/color control/green
  (changes colorpreset to custom)
  OK

0x1a blue
  setting, 0-64, regular
  osd path: color/color control/blue
  (changes colorpreset to custom)
  OK

0x1e auto
  trigger, base: 0, persistent (only if finished)
  1 -> auto adjustment, slow
    equivalent to the auto button on the monitor face
    takes approximately 4.5 or 2 seconds
    (see notes at 0xe2)
    displays a progress bar
  2 -> auto adjustment, fast
    takes approximately 0.5 seconds
    displays a progress bar, but jumps from 0% to 100%
