  1, 6 and 7 map to 2 (english)
  changing this setting (even identically) saves all
  settings using 0xb0/1 (but monitor led does not blink)
  besides making this setting persistent, this also means that
  other changes meant to be transient are also saved
  this is a perhaps unwanted side-effect
  throws IR (except for 0 and 8 which do nothing)
  TODO: IR

0xd6 dpms
  setting, 1-4, transient
  enables or disables dpms standby
  1 -> on
  4 -> standby
  2 and 3 map to 4 (standby)
  throws IR
  TODO: IR

0xdc magicbright
  setting, 1-4, regular
  1 -> text
  2 -> internet
  3 -> entertain
  4 -> custom
