  setting, 0-2, transient
  0 monitor face buttons are fully functional
  1 osd can't be opened, pressing any button on the monitor face
    (except for soft-off) displays a 'MagicTune' popup instead
    of its regular function
    used by official utility to avoid changing the settings on the
    osd while it is running
