Hi,

I'm using DDCcontrol 0.4.1 on a gentoo system with kernel
2.6.15-gentoo-r1. I have a Fujitsu Siemens P19-2 which, according to
http://ddccontrol.sourceforge.net/doc/0.4/apb.html, should be supported
by DDCcontrol 0.4.1. My graphics card is a NVidia GeForce FX 5700 which
should also be supported according to the "nVidia cards support table"
at http://ddccontrol.sourceforge.net/doc/0.4/apcs02.html.

When I use "ddccontrol -p", it says:



