If I use "gddccontrol", I again get 3 lines saying "Invalid response,
magic is 0x23" at the console. The monitor name detected is corrected,
but there's nothing to adjust in the window.

The output of "LANG= LC_ALL= ddccontrol -p -c -d" is appended to the end
of this mail if you should need it.

Do you know what's going wrong here?

Thanks in advance!

Cheers,

Michael.



